    div.ui.segment
      h3.ui.header About Legalizing Sex Work:
      p This Legalizing Sex Work policy calls for the United States to not to criminally penalize any person--adult or minor--for selling his or her own sexual services. Additionally, the U.S. should not criminally penalize those who purchase sexual services from adults.
    div.ui.segment
